timing_disable_nochange_checks(25.10)    timing_disable_nochange_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_nochange_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_nochange_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false (performs checks)

       When  set to true, disables no change timing model checks during timing
       analysis.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

